    <h1>Save Rate</h1>
    <p class="description">The percentage of viewers who bookmark your content out of total impressions. On Instagram and Pinterest, a high save rate is one of the strongest signals that your post has <strong>lasting reference value</strong> — and the algorithm rewards it with extended reach.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
